trans-unit.source: Holds text, markup, and server controls to render to a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentPlaceHolder"></xref> control in a master page.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder tekst, markup og server kontroller skal gjengi i en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentPlaceHolder"> </xref> kontrollen i en hoveddokumentet.

trans-unit.source: A Content control is a container for the content and controls of a content page.
trans-unit.target: En innhold kontroll er en beholder for innhold og kontroller av innhold-siden.

trans-unit.source: A Content control is used only with a master page that defines a corresponding <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentPlaceHolder> control.
trans-unit.target: En innhold kontroll bare brukes med en hoveddokumentet som definerer en tilsvarende <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentPlaceHolder>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentPlaceHolder>

trans-unit.source: A Content control is not added to the control hierarchy at runtime.
trans-unit.target: En innhold kontroll er ikke lagt til kontrollen hierarkiet under kjøring.

trans-unit.source: Instead, the contents within the Content control are directly merged into the corresponding <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentPlaceHolder> control.
trans-unit.target: I stedet innholdet i innhold kontrollen direkte sammen i den tilsvarende <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentPlaceHolder>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentPlaceHolder>

trans-unit.source: The Content control is associated with a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentPlaceHolder> using its <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Content.ContentPlaceHolderID%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Innhold kontrollen er knyttet til en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentPlaceHolder>ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Content.ContentPlaceHolderID%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Content.ContentPlaceHolderID%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentPlaceHolder>

trans-unit.source: Set the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Content.ContentPlaceHolderID%2A> property to the value of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ID%2A> property of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentPlaceHolder> control in a master page.
trans-unit.target: Angi den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Content.ContentPlaceHolderID%2A>egenskapen med verdien for den <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ID%2A>for en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentPlaceHolder>kontrollen i en.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentPlaceHolder> </xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ID%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Content.ContentPlaceHolderID%2A>

trans-unit.source: When the URL of the content page is called, all text, markup, and server controls that are contained within the Content control are rendered to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentPlaceHolder> on the master page, and the address bar of the browser will show the name of the content page.
trans-unit.target: Når URL-adressen til siden innhold kalles, alle text, markup og server kontroller som finnes i innhold kontrollen gjengis til den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentPlaceHolder>på hoveddokumentet og adressen i leseren viser navnet på siden innhold.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentPlaceHolder>

trans-unit.source: For more information about master pages and content pages, see [ASP.NET Master Pages](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Du finner mer informasjon om master sider og innhold sider [ASP.NET Master sider](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Content> control typically is created declaratively, not programmatically.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Content>kontrollen vanligvis er opprettet deklarativt, ikke programmatisk.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Content>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the ID of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentPlaceHolder"></xref> control that is associated with the current content.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir IDen for den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentPlaceHolder"> </xref> kontrollen som er knyttet til gjeldende innhold.

trans-unit.source: All content that is encapsulated by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Content> control renders within the referenced <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentPlaceHolder> control in a master page.
trans-unit.target: Alt innhold som er innkapslet av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Content>kontrollen gjengir i den refererte <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentPlaceHolder>kontrollen i en hoveddokumentet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentPlaceHolder> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Content>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Content> control is not added to the control hierarchy at runtime.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Content>kontrollen er ikke lagt til kontrollen hierarkiet under kjøring.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Content>

trans-unit.source: This property cannot be set by themes or style sheet themes.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen kan ikke angis ved oppsett eller stil arket Oppsett.
